You will definitely need to profile/optimize and hand code some queries.  I ran into a bad one a while back (2.2.2):<p><pre><code>   @foo = Foo.create
   @bars = Bar.find_all_by_some_attribute(:a)
   @foo.bars = @bars #--> slow!
</code></pre>
